data.description: Great location with easy access to major highways.  This beautiful move-in ready home features 3 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. The open floor plan has numerous upgrades including custom trim, granite counters, ventilation hood, backsplash, gutters, and newer driveway. The main floor features an open entertaining area as well as flex space for an office. The primary bedroom has a private bathroom with separate shower and tub, huge walk in closet, and walks thru to the laundry room. Enjoy your evening on a private patio or visit the shops and restaurants nearby!
